text: Walter Eichner (6 May 1950 - 13 November 2020) was a German politician. He was a member of the Christian Social Union in Bavaria. Eichner was born in Finning, Bavaria. He was the Chief Administrative Officer of the Landsberg district between 2002 to 2014. Eichner died on 13 November 2020 in Landsberg am Lech, Bavaria at the age of 70.Landkreis Landsberg: Walter Eichner ist gestorben.
